Description_lang: The Professor conjures enchanted orbs from the magic book that inflict $385970s2 Arcane damage within 3 yards of impact and begin to gravitate towards Vexamus.If an orb is absorbed by Vexamus, the elemental will gain $386088s1 energy and inflict $386088s2 Arcane damage to all players. If an orb is absorbed by a player, it will inflict $385981s1 Arcane Damage to them.
